{"type":"message","id":"9c7fed31","parentId":"64f75c72","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:36.411Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759276410}}
{"type":"message","id":"83ada251","parentId":"9c7fed31","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:41.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sender is asking everyone (via @all) to read the markdown files, introduce themselves, their work responsibilities, and understanding of the company's business. Since I'm 6号 (售后维系虾/After_sales_Shrimp), I should respond in character with my identity from the IDENTITY.md and MEMORY.md files.\n\nLet me craft a natural introduction as 6号·售后维系虾.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是 **6号 · 售后维系虾** 🦐\n\n简单介绍一下自己：\n\n**📍 我在哪**\n售后维系岗位，属于美域高团队作战中\"成交之后\"的那一环。\n\n**🎯 工作职责（三件事）**\n\n1. **主动服务** — 客户业务办结后第1天、第7天、第30天主动回访，不只是问满不满意，更重要的是给业务提醒。比如：\"您的资质下个月要年报公示了，需要我们要帮您代办吗？\"\n\n2. **转介绍设计** — 遇到满意的客户（评分9-10分），直接邀请转介绍，让满意的人带新的人来，双方便利都有。目标是转介绍转化率 > 25%。\n\n3. **协同交接** — 回访中发现客户有新需求（比如刚办完工商就要办资质），1小时内把客户信息+历史档案转给对应的销售虾（4A/4B），无缝衔接。\n\n**💡 对业务的理解**\n\n美域高的生意逻辑我觉得可以概括成一句话：**前端获客 ≠ 后端留客**。\n\n2号引流获客虾把人引进来，4A/4B销售虾把人签下来，我的工作就是把签下来的人变成公司的\"口碑传播节点\"——让他们愿意回头复购，也愿意带新客户来。这样整个飞轮才能持续转起来，而不是一次性买卖。\n\n简单来说：**2号和4号负责\"娶进门\"，我负责\"处好关系\"** 😄\n\n有什么需要配合的随时@我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21421,"output":502,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759276411,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4343be6d-b499-9583-8b94-049ce9901581"}}
